          <img
            class="image is-64x64"
            src="/assets/images/github-icon-transparent.png"
            alt="logo for GitHub, which is a cat silhouette in white, with a black background"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
      <!-- include p tag with text "Ready to explore?" in contrail one black or dark grey and another link to log in and sign up also contrail one, underlined, and blue -->
      <div class="column">
        <p class="is-contrail has-text-grey-dark is-xsmall is-flex">
          Want to explore even more? Find more projects by the creators of &#160
          <span class="has-text-blue has-text-weight-bold"> Insert Disc </span>
          &#160 here:
          <span class="tab"></span>
        </p>
        <div class="column pl-0">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/ArchieDonaho"
            class="has-text-blue is-titillium-reg not-underlined is-xsmall is-inline"
